body:
#### PR description:

This is a follow-up to https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/36129
Goals:
   * address comment https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/36129#pullrequestreview-811051764 ;
   * modernize code along latest recommendations;
   * equip plugins with `fillDescriptions` methods;
   * move plugins from `src` directory to `plugins`;
   * equip package with unit tests;
   * speed-up script for multi-IOV update of the triggerbits by using `multiprocessing`;
  
#### PR validation:

Relies on the updated unit tests.

